# ─── WisperLocal: top-level ignore ───────────────────────────────
# This folder is a distribution layout: the installer + docs sit here,
# and the full project lives in "Source Code/".

# NOTE: the top-level WisperLocal-Setup-X.Y.Z.exe installer is intentionally
# tracked so users can download it from the repo. (For a leaner repo you could
# instead publish it as a GitHub Release and ignore it here.)

# Personal speech-to-text dictation output — never upload
Data/
Source Code/Data/

# Python virtual environment
Source Code/.venv/
.venv/
venv/

# Build artifacts
Source Code/build/
Source Code/dist/
Source Code/installer_output/
build/
dist/
installer_output/

# Python caches
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.egg-info/
.eggs/

# Model cache / logs (if placed in-tree)
models/
*.log

# OS / editor cruft
Thumbs.db
.DS_Store
*.swp
.idea/
.vscode/
